It’s also important that you have a decent map, as no one in Guinea has a phone and rely on the paper maps I help carry around if I need to get anywhere quicker than I can walk. It has taken me seven months to figure out how to navigate this part of Conakry, Guinea.

Finally, know your address, which is critical. It is Safe World’s official address is Sante Garde Guinea Rue 635 – Prisbesion Guinée (rue). Safe World’s official name is Per Conseils de Basis pour le Developement of Sante Garde De L’Afrique L’ Ubuntu – Sante Garde Unity of the Brazilian Hemispheres Health Le.

Yes, these addresses, are difficult, and uncomfortable to say, but you’ve got to be thankful for them as it gives you a place to find news, and feel comfortable. The truth is, Safe World is not always welcomed in Guinea, but we keep trying, every person, every department, office, or room. We persist, and we do not give in, we have fought a battle for leadership in Guinea that will Improve on everyone’s health.
